    slug: "meray-pyary-rasool-saw-imported",
    description: `Meray Pyary Rasool SAW (My Beloved Prophet, peace be upon him) is an imported, high-quality Urdu-language book that presents the life and character of Prophet Muhammad (peace be upon him) in a format that emphasises the deep love and reverence that Muslims hold for the final messenger of Allah. This imported edition is distinguished by its superior production quality, featuring premium paper, excellent printing, and a durable binding that reflects the dignity and importance of its subject matter. The book is organised as a comprehensive biography that covers the entire span of the Prophet's life, from the events surrounding his blessed birth in Makkah through his childhood and youth, his marriage to Khadijah, his receipt of the first revelation in the Cave of Hira, the trials of the Makkan period, the migration to Madinah, the establishment of the Islamic state, the battles and treaties, the Farewell Pilgrimage, and his final illness and passing. What distinguishes this biography from many others is its emphasis on conveying the personal qualities and human dimensions of the Prophet that inspired such deep love and loyalty in his companions and that continue to inspire Muslims today. The book describes the Prophet's physical appearance in detail, drawing upon the descriptions of his companions, his gentle and kind demeanour, his sense of humour, his love for children, his generosity towards the poor, his patience in the face of hardship, his courage in battle, his humility despite his exalted position, and his tenderness towards his family. Each chapter includes hadith narrations that illustrate these qualities, allowing the reader to develop a vivid and intimate understanding of the Prophet's character. The book also addresses the Prophet's relationship with different segments of society — his treatment of women, children, the elderly, the poor, the slaves, and the non-Muslims under his protection — showing how his example established standards of justice, compassion, and human dignity that were revolutionary for their time and that remain relevant today. The imported edition's enhanced production quality makes this book suitable as a gift and as a treasured addition to any home library. The clear Urdu prose and the systematic organisation of the material make this biography accessible to readers at all levels. Whether read for personal spiritual growth, for teaching children about the Prophet, or as a gift to share the beauty of the Prophet's character with others, this edition of Meray Pyary Rasool serves as a powerful vehicle for increasing love and understanding of the final messenger of Allah.`,
    metaDescription: "Meray Pyary Rasool SAW imported edition is a premium Urdu biography of Prophet Muhammad emphasising his noble character with superior production quality."
